  ('dietitian-moex-11384', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-093-da9d23a3', 'sub-dietitian-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何者不是理想的冷凍食品（frozen food）之解凍（thawing）方法？ 置於冷藏庫中解凍  以微波爐解凍  將冷凍食品直接烹煮  放置於水槽內解凍', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:59+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "019192853fdc", "answer_pdf_sha1": "3763ec3c90be", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "093120", "c": "112", "s": "6001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "食品衛生與安全", "year": "093", "exam_name": "093年第二次專技醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、呼吸治療師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 35, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-11385', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-093-da9d23a3', 'sub-dietitian-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關食品調理作業區「空調（air conditioning）」的敘述，何者正確？ 所謂的「空調」只要能將空氣冷卻即可  空調系統不需要具有過濾的功能 「空調」設備需要有調節濕度的功能  可以用排油煙設備取代以節省成本', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:59+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "019192853fdc", "answer_pdf_sha1": "3763ec3c90be", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "093120", "c": "112", "s": "6001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "食品衛生與安全", "year": "093", "exam_name": "093年第二次專技醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、呼吸治療師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 36, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-11386', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-093-da9d23a3', 'sub-dietitian-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關「河豚中毒」的敘述，何者正確？ 河豚所有的組織及器官均有毒素存在  河豚毒素的熱安定性不佳，煮沸即可破壞 河豚毒素是一種神經毒素    河豚毒素已經有抗毒素可作為解藥', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:59+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "019192853fdc", "answer_pdf_sha1": "3763ec3c90be", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "093120", "c": "112", "s": "6001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "食品衛生與安全", "year": "093", "exam_name": "093年第二次專技醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、呼吸治療師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 37, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-11387', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-093-da9d23a3', 'sub-dietitian-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '台灣地區所發生的「西施舌貝」中毒是一種： 麻痺性貝毒素  腹瀉性貝毒素  肝毒性貝毒素  嘔吐性貝毒素', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:59+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "019192853fdc", "answer_pdf_sha1": "3763ec3c90be", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "093120", "c": "112", "s": "6001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "食品衛生與安全", "year": "093", "exam_name": "093年第二次專技醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、呼吸治療師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 38, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-11388', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-093-da9d23a3', 'sub-dietitian-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何者不是預防「黴菌毒素（mycotoxins）」中毒的理想方法？ 穀物採收後迅速將水分含量降至13%以下  於低溫、高相對溼度下儲存食品 添加防止黴菌生長之藥劑    減少食用發酵食品', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:59+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "019192853fdc", "answer_pdf_sha1": "3763ec3c90be", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "093120", "c": "112", "s": "6001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "食品衛生與安全", "year": "093", "exam_name": "093年第二次專技醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、呼吸治療師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 39, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-11389', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-093-da9d23a3', 'sub-dietitian-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '硼砂是違法的食品添加物，下列有關硼砂之敘述，何者正確？ 是一種人工甜味劑    又稱為吊白塊 是已知最強的致癌物    常非法添加於年糕、鹼粽、魚丸等食物中', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:59+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "019192853fdc", "answer_pdf_sha1": "3763ec3c90be", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "093120", "c": "112", "s": "6001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "食品衛生與安全", "year": "093", "exam_name": "093年第二次專技醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、呼吸治療師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 40, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-11390', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-093-da9d23a3', 'sub-dietitian-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '禽肉（poultry）及碎肉（stuffed meat）必需烹調至中心溫度多少℃至少15秒，才可被認為安全？', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:59+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "66a40bb85066", "answer_pdf_sha1": "ef42fcd1b56b", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "093020", "c": "112", "s": "6001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "食品衛生與安全", "year": "093", "exam_name": "093年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、呼吸治療師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 1, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
